org.chocosolver.samples.statistical.modelfit.timeseries

Class AR1TimeSeriesFit

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.chocosolver.samples.AbstractProblem
      • org.chocosolver.samples.statistical.modelfit.timeseries.AR1TimeSeriesFit

  • public class AR1TimeSeriesFit
extends org.chocosolver.samples.AbstractProblem
    We consider an AR(1) stochastic process and try to fit its parameters. This problem is discussed in R. Rossi, O. Agkun, S. Prestwich, A. Tarim, "Declarative Statistics," arxiv:1708.01829, Section 5.2
    Author:
    Roberto Rossi
